-- India's Essar Says It's Preferred Bidder For 60% of Zimbabwe Iron & Steel
-- B y   R a k t e e m   K a t a k e y
-- 2010-11-09T12:47:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/india-s-essar-says-it-s-preferred-bidder-for-60-of-zimbabwe-iron-steel.html
India’s Essar Group said it is the
preferred bidder for the Zimbabwe government’s 60 percent stake
in Zimbabwe Iron and Steel Co., according to an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rakteem Katakey in New Delhi at 
